The '''Wheel Security Force''' or more simply '''Wheel Security''' were the [[Law enforcement agency/Legends|local police]] of the [[Space station/Legends|space station]] known as [[The Wheel/Legends|The Wheel]].

==History==
They answered to [[Administrator/Legends|Administrator]] [[Simon Greyshade/Legends|Simon Greyshade]] and their job was to maintain order. They also handled situations beyond the abilities of [[Casino/Legends|casino]] [[Bouncer (occupation)/Legends|bouncers]]. Officers were usually [[Human/Legends|Human]] and wore a green and yellow uniform with enclosed helmets. Their armament included [[Force pike/Legends|shock rods]] and [[Blaster/Legends|blasters]].

